summary: HI! Just wanted to make a quick post for an announcement. I’m currently doing commissions until august 20th and I wanted to make...
caption:
HI! Just wanted to make a quick post for an announcement.

I’m currently doing commissions until august 20th and I wanted to make a post showing my three fave commissions i’ve done this summer as examples :)
I’ve recently wanted to start taking furry commissions, but I dont have a reason to draw furries for my own but I have a feeling it wont be hard for me cos I already draw demons and animals a lot?

So, here’s the deal, If you want to commission me to draw your fursona/furry oc, i’ll take the price down to $80 (full rendered illustration) for the first 2 people that contact me and after that, if all goes well, the price will go up to $100 for furry commissions (just because I do a lot of color detailing with fur and its time consuming…..). You can also ask me for flat color and we’ll talk about pricing :)

email me at gacpars@gmail.com
